arStrings.szText: The Dregs who overwhelmed the ruins west of Necropolis have filled the lower chambers with corpses. Itâ€™s unknown why Dregs amass bodies in such a way, but several scholars suppose it to be a bizarre form of art.

If Necropolis is ever to be returned to Rathma's faithful, the Dregs must be driven out of the surrounding lands. I travel now to clear those ruins and investigate the pit of corpses. May Rathma defend me.
